This paper is about improving the performance prediction of IDA* algorithm, which is a search algorithm commonly used in artificial intelligence and computer science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with the analysis of the search tree and the distribution of heuristic values, which are topics related to data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper proposes a new formula for predicting the performance of IDA* algorithm, which involves statistical analysis and machine learning techniques, making it relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG).
